        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "INVISIBLE INK PENS: If you need to stealthily communicate covert written messages or are trying to avoid a digital footprint, look no further than the ASR Federal Security Spy UV Invisible Ink Permanent Marker Pens; Ideal for making sensitive notes, marking personal property and theft detection, the permanent marker pens will come in handy in all sorts of espionage situations",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "ELECTION CERTIFIED: Used by local and federal government agencies; election certified invisible ink pens and markers for voting stations and election related events; the markings will remain invisible until illuminated under a UV light",
