                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "UNDETECTABLE PERSONAL SECURITY: Due to the nature of the invisible ink, you can mark some of your most valuable personal property without damage; if altered or tampered with, reveal with a UV light or black light source",
